additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Read safety directions. For advice contact a Poisons Information Centre (phone Australia 13 11 26 or New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If swallowed, DO NOT induce vomiting. If in eyes, hold eyelids apart and flush continuously with running water. Continue flushing until advised to stop by the Poisons Information Centre or a doctor, or for at least 15 minutes. If skin or hair contact occurs remove contaminated clothing and flush skin and hair with running water.
